[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 4.0,
    "text": "The following contains clips from Disney's The Little Mermaid, now available on Blu-ray and DVD."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "I just don't know what we're going to do with you, young lady."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "Daddy, I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "I just forgot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "As a result of your careless behavior..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "Careless and reckless behavior..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.0,
    "endTime": 18.0,
    "text": "The entire celebration was..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "Well, it was ruined."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "That's all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.0,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "Completely destroyed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "This concert was to be the pinnacle of my distinguished career."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 32.0,
    "text": "Now, thanks to you, I am the laughingstock of the entire kingdom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.0,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "But it wasn't her fault."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "Uh, well, first, uh, the shark chases."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "Yeah, yeah, and we tried to..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "But we couldn't, and he didn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "Grr!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "And we..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "Ah, and then we were safe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "But then the seagull came, and it was this is this, and that is that, and..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "Seagull?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "Oh, you went up to the surface again, didn't you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "Didn't you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "Nothing happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 63.0,
    "text": "Oh, Ariel, how many times must we go through this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.0,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "You could have been seen by one of those barbarians, by one of those humans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "Daddy, they're not barbarians."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "They're dangerous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "Do you think I want to see my youngest daughter snared by some fish-eater's hook?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "I'm 16 years old."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.0,
    "endTime": 77.0,
    "text": "I'm not a child anymore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "Don't you take that tone of voice with me, young lady."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "Well..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "As long as you live under my ocean, you'll obey my rules."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "But if you would just listen..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "Not another word!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "And I am never, never to hear of you going to the surface again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 91.0,
    "text": "Is that clear?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "Teenagers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "They think they know everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "You give them an inch, they swim all over you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "Do you think I was too hard on her?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 112.0,
    "text": "Definitely not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "Why, if Ariel was my daughter, I'd show her who was boss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "None of this flipping to the surface and all of such nonsense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "No, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "I keep her under tight control."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "You're absolutely right, Sebastian."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.0,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "Of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "Ariel needs constant supervision."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 130.0,
    "text": "Constant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "Someone to watch over her, to keep her out of trouble."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "All the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": " And you are just the crab to do it."
  }
]